---
title: Goats Cheese Crostini with Chick Pea Salad, Tomatoes and Zaatar
description: Today's dish is a feast of contrasting flavours and textures. Creamy goat's cheese sits on top of a crunchy garlic-scented crostini and ripe tomatoes mingle with nutty chickpeas. As if that wasn't enough, you'll be finishing everything off with some charred courgette slices and a sprinkling of fragrant zahtar. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/goats-cheese-crostini-f5bde1e4.jpg
